    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The phenomenon of weak linking between molecules, particularly water molecules or other molecules with a hydroxyl group, such as alcohols.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
